clause.text:
footwear with outer soles not over 3.5 mm
				in thickness, consisting of cellular rubber, non-grain leather, or textile
				material;

row.entry:
Footwear valued over $2.50/pair (other than footwear for women;
						house slippers; and tennis shoes, basketball shoes, gym shoes, training shoes
						and the like) (provided for in subheading 6403.99.90)
